\f2\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Ps::0>
\f0 Since Schaeffer\'92s writing there has been little academic investigation into areas that might illuminate the answer to some or all of his questions. The conclusion of Schaeffer\'92s work is yet to be discovered, \'93\'85a treatise, not on musical objects, but on the musical work!\'94  (Chion 1983, 3). I am yet unable to offer a treatise on the musical work, but the structural analysis I have conducted on the research of others, as well as my own has largely been done where most academics have so far shamefully deigned to look \'97 in those disciplines deemed loosely related to music, unacademic, fringe, etc. These disciplines included the study of myth, the Jungian concepts of the collective unconscious and dream interpretation, and psychedelic drugs. Within these disciplines is precisely where Schaeffer\'92s treasure is to be found. What follows then, in this section is a map of the territory as I understand it, balancing between adherence to a common thread of music, and the creative proclivity, and necessity to wander. \
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://15BA233D-35B2-4DD2-ADBC-874E0ED460C7"}}{\fldrslt The four interrelated starting points for this research will be presented first.}} I will explain their interrelatedness to each other. While establishing the interrelatedness of these initial disciplines, I will provide information on how these topics are synthesized into story. Finally, I will detail the conclusions reached in the course of this research, generalize the emergent approach, and present impetus for moving forward with this more story-centric approach to music making. In order to retain the common thread of music throughout, musical examples from the compositions of others, as well as my own will be given as examples for concepts being detailed. If one is to consider the totality of the framework that I have constructed as a geometrical form, each topic will serve to form a mold, or impression of part of the overall framework\'92s surface. It is interesting to note that the information must be unfolded in this vignetted manner despite the fact that all component topics suggest story, in a linear sense, to be the connecting feature.\
